170
00:16:28.380 --> 00:16:28.420
Kamijiro 
Holdem's Stomach

171
00:16:28.420 --> 00:16:28.460
Kamijiro 
Holdem's Stomach

172
00:16:28.460 --> 00:16:28.500
Kamijiro 
Holdem's Stomach

173
00:16:28.500 --> 00:16:28.550
Kamijiro 
